{"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"title":"Getting Started with OUDS","roleHeading":"Article","images":[{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"card"}],"role":"article"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Integrate OUDS"},{"anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Use Swift Package Manager"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0-rc3"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Import the librairies you need"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"text":" products.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets."}]}],"name":"Tip","style":"tip"},{"code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}]},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above and all themes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Chose your theme","anchor":"Chose-your-theme"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" framework provides today four themes:","type":"text"}]},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Theme"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Compact"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For Sosh products"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Apply a theme","anchor":"Apply-a-theme"},{"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}]}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"]}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2},{"numberOfColumns":2,"type":"row","columns":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one "},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"name":"Tip","type":"aside","style":"tip"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you use Xcode "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the "},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Essentials","title":"Essentials"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Themes":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/themes","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Themes"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are applications of specific values for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"components tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and dimensionsemantic tokens_ using in the end "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"type":"text","text":" contains any relevant tokens which can be used for components rendering."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"type":"text","text":" can use its own assets like fonts and icons."}],"title":"Themes","role":"article","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png"}],"kind":"article"},"ic_theme_intro.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_them